00:28:57,299 --> 00:28:58,500
Ya, Pak Kim.

245
00:28:58,799 --> 00:29:00,840
Kalau begitu, ayo kita makan seolleongtang bersama.

246
00:29:22,929 --> 00:29:23,989
Bong Gil,

247
00:29:24,659 --> 00:29:26,760
aku sudah mendengar idemu,

248
00:29:27,260 --> 00:29:29,130
tapi sekarang bukan saat yang tepat.

249
00:29:30,469 --> 00:29:34,299
Tentara Jepang menyatakan invasi Shanghai sebagai kemenangan.

250
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:36,169
Lihat keadaan kita.

251
00:29:36,539 --> 00:29:39,010
Kita bersembunyi di Konsesi Prancis.

252
00:29:39,280 --> 00:29:40,880
Apa yang bisa kita lakukan?

253
00:29:43,809 --> 00:29:46,049
"Seolleongtang Joseon"

254
00:29:47,849 --> 00:29:49,989
"Jangbuchulga saengbulhwan".

255
00:29:50,650 --> 00:29:52,190
Saat seorang pria meninggalkan rumahnya,

256
00:29:52,489 --> 00:29:54,719
dia tidak seharunsnya kembali sebelum mencapai tujuannya.

257
00:29:58,590 --> 00:30:01,799
Aku sudah memutuskan setelah mengetahui kematian Lee Bong Chang.

258
00:30:03,669 --> 00:30:04,830
Ini.

259
00:30:14,909 --> 00:30:18,580
"Pada 29 April 1932, perayaan kemenangan perang"

260
00:30:18,580 --> 00:30:21,979
"Dan perayaan ulang tahun Kaisar Jepang"

261
00:30:21,979 --> 00:30:25,250
"Akan diadakan di Taman Hongkou di Shanghai"

262
00:30:29,429 --> 00:30:31,859
29 April, Taman Hongkou.

263
00:30:33,760 --> 00:30:35,460
Di sanalah aku akan mati.

